    v0 = wp.abs((wp.cos(tmp + 0.65) - (v1 + 0.88 * tmp + 0.54)))
    v1 = v0
    v1 = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.01) - 0.45) - wp.exp(wp.cos(v1 + 0.19)))
    tmp = wp.abs(v1)
    v2 = 0.90
    v1 = 0.75
    v1 = (((v2 + 0.52 * v0 + 0.70) * (v2 + 0.31 / v1 + 0.43)) / (wp.exp(v1 + 0.82) + v1))
